\id PHP - Zanaki Philippians
\h Abhafiripi
\toc3 Abhafiripi
\toc2 Abhafiripi
\toc1 Enyaarubha ya Pauro ku Bhafiripi
\mt2 Enyaarubha ya Pauro ku
\mt1 Bhafiripi
\imt1 Obhutaangiro
\ip Enyaarubha yino yakaamirwe na Pauro, omuhokya wa Taatabhugya, akakaamira ekanisa yino eri mumugye gwa Firipi. Erarorekana kubha Pauro akakaama enyaarubha yino hano yaari mukibhoho mumugye gwa Rooma. Pauro akabhakaamira Abhakrisito bhano bhaari bhamwiikiriirye Krisito Yeesu. Hano Pauro yahikiri kweebho, akabharwaazira Amangʼana Amazomu. Ibhaga riindi Abhakrisito bhayo nibho bhakeerekya obhuseegi ku Pauro no okumusakirya kumeendi gaaye.
\ip Obhugirirye bhwa Pauro okubhakaamira enyaarubha yino yaari arabhabhuurira, “Muzomirye Abhafiripi,” kubhusakirya bhuno bhakaruusya kweewe okuhitira ku Epafurodito. Kweeki, akeenda kubheerekeererya amangʼana go okukora no okubhatoongera amanaga okubha bhabhe bharatuniirira ekireengyo kya Yeesu Krisito kwo okwiikongʼeererya. Eriingʼana eriindi rino yeendiri kubhabhuurira ryaari okubharekya bhatiikirirya ameegyo mabhiihu ga Abhayahudi gano gaabhakoriri okutaamania na abhiikirirya mukanisa yaabhu.
\ip Enyaarubha yino emenyekeeni kubha ni nyaarubha yo obhuzomererwa kwo okubha muusi wamu eriiseego ryo obhuzomererwa ririikyoorera maanga maaru. Obhuzomererwa bhuyo bhugumire kubhiikirirya bha Krisito Yeesu.
\c 1
\s1 Obhukeerya
\p 
\v 1 Enyaarubha yino nikaamiri enye Pauro, hamwe na Timoteo, omugya omurikyaane wa Krisito Yeesu. Turabhakaamira abhiimeerereri na abhasakirya bhe ekanisa, na neemwe abhahoreeru\f + \fr 1:1 \fk Abhahoreeru\ft . Rora engʼana yino mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* abhaandi bhoosi kwo okugwaatana na Krisito Yeesu, bhano mukwiikara mumugye gwa Firipi.
\p 
\v 2 Orubhaango no omureembe okurwa ku Taatabhugya Taata weetu, na ku Mukuru weetu Yeesu Krisito, bhibhe neemwe.
\s1 Pauro arabhasabhira Abhafiripi
\p 
\v 3 Eriibhaga ryoosi hano nikubhahiita emwe, niramubhuurira Taatabhugya, “Ozomirye, Omukuru waane.”
\v 4 Kweeki, eriibhaga ryoosi hano nikubhasabhira, nirabhasabhira kwo obhuzomererwa,
\v 5 kwo okubha emwe mugwaateeni neenye okuraarika Amangʼana Amazomu, kweema orusiku runo mukiigwa no okwiikirirya tee reero.
\v 6 Nino obhuheene kubha Taatabhugya wuno yataangiri emirimo emizomu muziikoro zyeenyu, aragigeendererya tee gikuunaane kwo orusiku runo Krisito Yeesu araakyoore.
\p 
\v 7 Ni bhuzomu niiseege gano iguru weenyu mwoosi, kwo okubha nibhaseegiri bhukongʼu. Muragwaatana murubhaango rwa Taatabhugya hamwe neenye, eraabhe nibhohirwe mukibhoho kisya eraabhe niriisasaama no okumenyeekererya Amangʼana Amazomu.
\v 8 Taatabhugya amenyiri kubha niragaamba obhuheene, hano nikukumiirirya kubha niriigoomba bhukongʼu okurorena neemwe kweeki. Nibhaseegiri emwe kwo obhuseegi bhuryabhurya, kyeego Krisito Yeesu abhaseegiri.
\p 
\v 9 Nirabhasabhira ku Taatabhugya kubha obhuseegi bhweenyu bhugeenderere kwaaruha bhukongʼu, kweeki mubhe na amangʼeeni no obhumenyeekererya,
\v 10 okubha mubhone okugiikirirya gano gano obhweera. Hayo niho murabha abhaheene, murabha mutana amasoro tee orusiku rurya Krisito araakyoore.
\v 11 Obhwiikari bhweenyu bhuriizura amangʼana ge eheene, gano gakubhoneka kuhitira Krisito Yeesu. Gayo goosi gamuguungye no okumukumya Taatabhugya.
\s1 Okwiikara ni kumuhokeerya Krisito
\p 
\v 12 Ambe, abhahiiri bhaane, ndeenda mumenye bhuzomu kubha gano gaambweeni, gasakiirye bhukongʼu kuraarika Amangʼana Amazomu.
\v 13 Kweego, abhariibhi bhoosi bhe enyuumba yo obhutemi, hamwe na abhaandi bhoosi, bhamenyiri kubha nibhohirwe kwo okubha niramuhokeerya Krisito.
\v 14 Hamwe na gayo, nimenyiri kubha okubhohwa kwaane eno, kubhakoriri abhiikirirya abharikyeetu bhaaru bhagumire eziikoro ku Mukuru Yeesu, naabhe bharabharwaazira abhaatu engʼana ya Taatabhugya kwa amanaga goosi, bhatana haho.
\p 
\v 15 Ni heene kubha, bhariho abhaandi bhano bhakurwaaza amangʼana ga Krisito kwo okubha bhano omugono na bharahizana neenye. Naabhe ego, bhariho abhaandi bhano bhakurwaaza kumiiseego amazomu.
\v 16 Bhano bhakukora ego kwo obhuseegi, eno bhamenyiri bhuzomu kubha Taatabhugya anituuriri mukibhoho okubha nimeererere Amangʼana Amazomu.
\v 17 Nawe bharya bho obhwiimani, bhararwaaza amangʼana ga Krisito kwe enzira yo okuhizana neenye, naabhe etari kwe ekoro nzomu. Bhareenda kwoongerya enyaako yaane mukibhoho.
\p 
\v 18 Nawe garasarikaki? Amangʼana ga Krisito gakurwaazwa, gabhe kumiiseego amabhi kasi kumiiseego mazomu. Neenye kwe ekigirirye kye eriingʼana riyo nirazomererwa. Kweeki, nirageenderera kubha no obhuzomererwa.
\v 19 Nimenyiri kubha mugoosi gano gambweeni, niratuuribhwa, kwo okubha muranisabhira ku Taatabhugya, ne Ekoro Muhoreeru\f + \fr 1:19 \fk Ekoro Muhoreeru\ft . Rora amangʼana gano mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* wa Yeesu Krisito aranisakirya.
\v 20 Niraganya kwe enaamba kuru no okwiisiga kubha, nitakusuukibhwa kwe enzira yoyoosi. Nawe kwo obhukaari bhwoosi, kyeego eziisiku zyoosi na bhoono egoego, Krisito aguungibhwe mugoosi gano nikukora, hano nikubha muhoru kasi nikuuri.
\p 
\v 21 Kweenye hano niraasaage muhoru nikumuhokeerya Krisito, na hano niraakwe, nirabha no obhweera bhukongʼu.
\v 22 Nawe niraageenderere kwiikara mukyaaro, nirageenderera kurora obhweera bhwe emirimo gino nikukora. Bhoono nisore riihe? Enye nitamenyiri!
\v 23 Nirarutwa gati wa amangʼana abhiri. Niriigoomba okurwa mukyaaro hano, ndeenda niikare hamwe na Krisito. Rino niryo rino obhweera bhukongʼu.
\v 24 Nawe ereenderwa kukiraho, enye nigeenderere kwiikara mukyaaro kwiiguru weenyu.
\v 25 Nino obhuheene bhwe engʼana yiyo, kweego nimenyiri kubha nirageenderera kwiikara mukyaaro. Kweeki, nirabha hamwe neemwe mwoosi, okubha nibhasakirye mukiine mubhwiikirirya bhweenyu no okubha no obhuzomererwa.
\v 26 Hano niraabhe hamwe neemwe, murabha ne ekigirirye kyo okurora enguungo iguru waane kwo okugwaatana na Krisito Yeesu, kwo okubha arabha anisakiirye nikyoore kweemwe.
\s1 Eteemo yeenyu etuniirire Amangʼana Amazomu
\p 
\v 27 Ambe, engʼana yino ekweenderwa ni kubha eteemwa yeenyu eriingʼaane na Amangʼana Amazomu iguru wa Krisito. Hano nikuuza kubharora kisya niritama kuuza, niigwe murageenderera kwiimeerera bhugumiru no okubha no obhumwe, kwe ekoro yimwe eno murarwaana eriihi ryo obhwiikirirya bhuno bhukutuukana na Amangʼana Amazomu.
\v 28 Mutabhoobhoha abhabhisa bheenyu kwe engʼana yoyoosi. Yiyo niyo eraabheerekye kubha ebho bhareerekera kusikibhwa, nawe emwe mureerekera kutuuribhwa. Gayo goosi ni mirimo gya Taatabhugya.
\v 29 Mutaheerwe okumwiikirirya Krisito omweene, nawe muheerwe naabhe okunyaakibhwa kwiiguru waaye.
\v 30 Muriitana eriihi riryarirya, rino niteeni naryo, kyeego mwaruuzi. Naabhe bhoono muriigwa kubha nirageenderera kwiitana naryo.
\c 2
\s1 Okweega obhusuuku bhwa Yeesu Krisito
\p 
\v 1 Awe, muratoongerwa ekoro kuriingʼaana no okubha abhaatu bha Krisito? Awe, muragosororibhwa no obhuseegi bhwaaye? Mbe, munabhwo obhugwaatani ne Ekoro Muhoreeru? Mbe, muraseegwa no okurorerwa ebhigoongi na Krisito?
\v 2 Eraabhe niigo eri, niho mukuunaanie obhuzomererwa bhwaane kwo okubha no obhwiigwaani no obhuseegi emwe kwe emwe. Kweeki, mubhe no obhumwe muziikoro zyeenyu na mubhe na amiiseego gamwe.
\v 3 Mutakora eriingʼana ryoryoosi kwe ekoro yo obhwiimani naabhe kwo obhwiizuungya. Nawe mubhe no obhusuuku no okubhara abhaandi kubha bhazomu kukira emwe abheene.
\v 4 Omuutu atiiseega amangʼana gaaye omweene ego, nawe kweeki yiiseege amangʼana ga abhaandi.
\p 
\v 5 Amiiseego geenyu gabhe garyagarya gano yaari nago Krisito Yeesu.
\q1 
\v 6 Yiingabha ewe kwe esimuka yaari Taatabhugya,
\q1 ataaruuzi ni kisi asaage agwaatiriiri riyo.
\q1 
\v 7 Nawe, ewe akaritiga riyo,
\q1 akiiyiikya, akabha kyeego omugya,
\q1 akiibhurwa mutuubho yo omuutu,
\q1 akabha omuutu.
\q1 
\v 8 Neewe akabha ne etuubho yo omuutu,
\q1 akiiyiikya,
\q1 akabha omwiigwa ku Taatabhugya,
\q1 akiikirirya okukwa,
\q1 naabhe kukwa kumusaraba!
\q1 
\v 9 Kweego Taatabhugya akamutiirya
\q1 iguru kukira ebhigiro bhyoosi,
\q1 akamuha eriina eriikuru kukira amariina goosi,
\q1 
\v 10 okubha kwo obhusuuku bhwe eriina rya Yeesu,
\q1 ebhigiro bhyoosi bhihigame kweewe,
\q1 bhya mwiisaaro,
\q1 bhya mukyaaro
\q1 na bhya nyaari.\f + \fr 2:10 \fk Nyaari\ft . Rora engʼana yino mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f*
\q1 
\v 11 Kweeki, abhaatu bhoosi bhiikirirye kubha
\q1 Yeesu Krisito ni Mukuru,
\q1 kwo obhuguungo bhwa Taatabhugya Taata.
\s1 Abhiikirirya bhabhe kyeego obhweero mukyaaro
\p 
\v 12 Awee, abhaseegwa bhaane, eriibhaga hano niari kweemwe, mwaari muramwiigwa Taatabhugya eziisiku zyoosi. Kweego ego, naabhe bhoono hano niri kure neemwe mugeenderere kukora gano gakweenderwa kubhaatu bhano Taatabhugya abhatuurirye. Mukore gayo kwo okurigita kuno kukutuukana no okumwoobhoha Taatabhugya.
\v 13 Ambe, mukore ego kwo okubha Taatabhugya niwe akukora emirimo muusi weenyu, okubha museege no okukora amangʼana gano akuseega gakorwe.
\p 
\v 14 Amangʼana goosi gano mukukora, mukore kutama kuririirira naabhe kuhakana.
\v 15 Kweego, mubhe abhaana bha Taatabhugya abhaheene bhano bhatari na amasoro. Kweeki, mubhe abhaatu bhano bhatakugaambwa bhubhi gati wa abhaatu bha bhoono bhano bhiizwiiri amabhi na bhano bhabhuriri. Gati wa abhaatu bhayo, emwe murorekane kyo obhweero bhuno bhukubhara mukyaaro.
\v 16 Kweeki, mubharwaazire abhaatu bhagumire mungʼana ya Taatabhugya yino ekubhaha obhuhoru bhwa kirakeego. Mukore ego okubha niizuungye murusiku runo Krisito araakyoore, kubha emirimo gino nikakora kwo omukya gati weenyu gitaari gya bhusa.
\p 
\v 17 Naabhe eraabhe obhuhoru bhwaane bhuraruusibhwa kye ekimweeso kya amaanzi go omuzabibu, hamwe no obhwiikirirya bhweenyu bhuno mukukora ekimweeso embere wa Taatabhugya, enye nirazomererwa. Obhuzomererwa bhuyo bhuragwaatana hamwe na neemwe mwoosi.
\v 18 Na neemwe muzomererwe egoego, kweeki muriiryaate hamwe neenye.
\s1 Pauro arabhatuma Timoteo na Epafurodito
\p 
\v 19 Omukuru Yeesu ariiseega, nine eriisigo kumuragania Timoteo hano haguhiigo, yiize kweemwe, okubha araakyoore eno, anitoongere ekoro hano akunibhuurira amangʼana geenyu.
\v 20 Kwo okubha nitana muutu wuundi wuno akubhamenya emwe heene heene kya Timoteo.
\v 21 Abhaandi bhoosi bharamenya amangʼana gaabhu abheene, bhatakumenya amangʼana ga Krisito Yeesu.
\v 22 Nawe mumenyiri kyeego Timoteo yiiyeerekirye kubha muutu muzomu. Ahokirye neenye mumirimo gyo okurwaaza Amangʼana Amazomu, kyeego omwaana na wiise waabhu.
\v 23 Kweego niriisiga kubha, niramuragania kweemwe okutama kukeezera bhwaangu hano niraamenye amangʼana gano garaanibhone.
\v 24 Kweeki, niriisiga kubha Omukuru Yeesu aranikiririirya enye niize kweemwe haguhiigo.
\p 
\v 25 Bhoono nirarora bhuzomu okumuragania kweemwe omwiikirirya omurikyaane Epafurodito, wuno akukora emirimo gya Taatabhugya hamwe neenye. Niwe omusirikare omurikyaane mwiihi ryo okwiitanira Amangʼana Amazomu. Kweeki, niwe mukamuragania kweenye okunisakirya no okunihokeerya mubhigiro bhino nikusuuhirwa.
\v 26 Niramuhaatira kwo okubha ewe ariigoomba kurorana neemwe mwoosi, kweeki, ekoro yaaye ene ebhigoongi kwo okubha mwiigwiiri yaari murweeri.
\v 27 Eheene yaari murweeri bhukongʼu, wo okukwa. Bhoono Taatabhugya akamurorera ebhigoongi, akamuhorya. Etaari kubha Taatabhugya yaari ne ebhigoongi kweewe omweene, nawe yaari ne ebhigoongi naabhe kweenye, okubha ebhigoongi bhyaane bhitiiyoongerya iguru ye ebhigoongi ebhiindi.
\p 
\v 28 Kwe ekigirirye kiyo, niramuragania kweemwe kwa bhwaangu, okubha hano mukumurora kweeki, muzomererwe ne ehaho yaane ehwe.
\v 29 Mumusuungʼaane kwo obhuseegi bhwo Omukuru Yeesu na kwo obhuzomererwa bhwoosi. Omuutu wowoosi kya wuyo, mumusuuke,
\v 30 kwo okubha yaari haguhi kukwa kwiiguru ye emirimo gya Krisito. Kweeki, yaari abhanwiiri okubhurya obhwiikari bhwaaye, okubha ahikye obhusakirya bhuno emwe mukatamwa okubhuhikya kweenye kwo okubha niari kure neemwe.
\c 3
\s1 Pauro aramwiisiga Krisito
\p 
\v 1 Mubhuteero, abhahiiri bhaane, muzomererwe kwo okugwaatana no Omukuru Yeesu. Amangʼana gano naamariri kubhakaamira, nitakurosa kukyoorera kubhakaamira, kwo okubha gayo ni kye engubha yeenyu yo obhwiikirirya.
\p 
\v 2 Mwiiriihe na abheegya bho orurimi bhano bhakusikirya emigiro gye Ekiyahudi mukanisa. Abheegya bhayo ni kye eziimbwa, ni bhano bhakutemya obhubhi, bharakumiirirya kubha otinwe niho otuuribhwe.
\v 3 Rora etwe nibho tusaarirwe kwe eheene na Taatabhugya, kwo okubha Ekoro Muhoreeru atusakiirye okumuseengera Taatabhugya. Etwe turiikumya iguru wa Krisito Yeesu no okumwiisiga. Kweeki, etwe tutakwiisiga amahokya geetu ge emibhiri okubhona obhutuurya,
\v 4 yiingabha enye omweene niinganagirye okwiisiga amangʼana go omubhiri. Eraabhe ariho omuutu wuno ariirora anago amahokya go omubhiri gano akunagya okwiisiga, enye ninago maaru go okwiisiga kukira ewe.
\v 5 Enye nikasaarwa orusiku rwa kanaane okurwa okwiibhurwa,\f + \fr 3:5a \xt Rora Obhweemero 17:12; Abharaawi 12:3.\xt*\f* nikarwa mukisyooko kya Benjamini, we ekyaaro kya Iziraeri. Enye ni Mweeburania eheene. Kwo okugigwaata emigiro gye Ekiyahudi, enye nikagigwaata bhuzomu, kwo okubha niari Mufarisayo.\f + \fr 3:5b \fk Mufarisayo\ft . Rora \ft \it Abhafarisayo\it* mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f*
\v 6 Kweeki, nikiigoomba bhukongʼu kukora gano nikiiseega kubha niigo Taatabhugya akweenda. Kiyo nikyo kyagirirye nikabhanyaakya Abhakrisito. Kwe eheene yino ekutuukana ne emigiro, niari nitana amasoro gogoosi.
\p 
\v 7 Nawe, gayo goosi gano niari kurora kubha gano obhweera, bhoono nirarora gatana bhweera kwo okumutuniirira Krisito.
\v 8 Naabhe gatari gayo ageene, nawe nirarora goosi kubha gatana bhweera okuriingʼaania no obhweera obhukuru bhwo okumumenya Krisito Yeesu, Omukuru waane. Kwiiguru waaye, nitigiri agaandi goosi. Nirabhara gayo kyo obhunyaka, okubha nibhe omuutu wa Krisito,
\v 9 na nigwaatane neewe. Nitakwiisigira kweeki, eheene yino ekurwa kwo okwiigwa emigiro, nawe eheene yirya yino ekurwa kwo okumwiikirirya Krisito. Eheene yiyo, erahaanwa na Taatabhugya kubhano bhamwiikiriirye Krisito.
\p 
\v 10 Ndeenda okumumenya Krisito kukiraho no okubha na amanaga gano gaamuryooriri Krisito kurwa mubhaku. Ndeenda obhugwaatani neewe munyaako yaaye no okutuubhana neewe muruku rwaaye.
\v 11 Ndeenda amangʼana gayo okubha nibhe gati wa abhaatu bhano Taatabhugya araabharyoore okurwa mubhaku.
\s1 Okwiikongʼeererya tee mubhuteero bhwe emirimo
\p 
\v 12 Enye nitakugaamba nimariri kuhikira obhuteero bhwa amangʼana gayo goosi, kasi nimariri kubha omuheene, zeyi, nawe nirageenderera kwo omukya okubha nibhone gayo. Gayo nigo Krisito Yeesu akaanibhirikirira nibhone.
\v 13 Abhahiiri bhaane, nitakwiibhara kubha nimariri okugwaata gayo. Nawe nirakora ekigiro kimwe, nitigiri okwiiseega gano gahitiri na nirakora omukya okubha nibhone gano gari embere.
\v 14 Nirageenderera kwo omukya okubha nihike mubhuteero no okuhaanwa esaambo yaane. Esaambo yiyo niyo embirikiro ya Taatabhugya kusikira mwiisaaro kwo okuhitira Krisito Yeesu.
\p 
\v 15 Kweego, etwe twoosi bhano tukongʼiri mukoro, tureenderwa kubha no obhukongʼeru bhuyobhuyo. Kyeego muna amiiseegi gano gatatuubheeni na amangʼana gano, Taatabhugya niwe arabhakuundukurira okubha mugamenye kyeego gari.
\v 16 Bhoono ekigiro ekikuru ni kubha tugye embere kwe enzira yiyoyiyo yino tuyiituniiriiri tee bhoono ego.
\s1 Abhiikirirya bheege eteemwa ya Pauro
\p 
\v 17 Abhahiiri bhaane, mwoosi mweege eteemo yaane. Kweeki, mweege kubhaatu bhano bhakutuniirira eteemwa yeetu.
\v 18 Nimariri kubhabhuurira maanga nzaru eriingʼana rino nikweenda kugaamba, bhoono nirarikyoorera kweeki naabhe kwe eziingusuri, bhariho abhaatu bhaaru kuteemo yaabhu bhariikara kya abhabhisa bho omusaraba gwa Krisito.
\v 19 Obhuteero bhwa abhaatu bhayo ni bhusikibhwa, enaamba yaabhu niyo Taatabhugya waabhu. Ebho bhariikumirya amahokya ge eziisoni gano bhakukora. Kweeki, bharakorera amangʼana ge ekyaaro ageene.
\p 
\v 20 Nawe, etwe ni bhiikari bha mwiisaaro na turaroreerera kwe enaamba ekuru yo okurwa eyo kwo Omutuurya, Omukuru Yeesu Krisito.
\v 21 Ewe anazyo eziinguru zyo okutuura ebhigiro bhyoosi bhibhe iyaasi wo obhukaangati bhwaaye. Kwe enzira ya amanaga gayo, arakyoosya emibhiri gyeetu gyo okunyoheera, gibhe no obhuguungo kyeego omubhiri gwaaye.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Kweego, abhahiiri bhaane, mwiimeerere bhugumiru kwo okumwiisiga Omukuru. Nibhaseegiri na niriigoomba okurorana neemwe, abharikyaane. Emwe ni bhuzomererwa bhwaane na ni saambo yaane yino niheerwe kwe emirimo gino nikoriri.
\s1 Obhurekya bhwa Pauro
\p 
\v 2 Nirabhiisasaama bhukongʼu Euodia na Sintike bhabhe na amiiseego gamwe, kwo okubha bhoosi bharamutuniirira Omukuru Yeesu.
\v 3 Naabhe awe omuhokya omurikyaane omuheene, nirasabha obhasakirye abhakari abhabhiri bhayo bhabhe na amiiseego gamwe. Bhayo bhoosi bhabhiri bhakakora omukya bhukongʼu hamwe neenye kwo okuraarika Amangʼana Amazomu iguru wa Krisito Yeesu. Kweeki, abhakari bhayo bhaari bharakora emirimo hamwe na Kirementi na abhahokya abharikyaane abhaandi. Amariina ga abhaatu bhayo bhoosi gakaamirwe mukitabhu kyo obhuhoru.
\p 
\v 4 Muzomererwe eziisiku zyoosi, kwo okugwaatana no Omukuru Yeesu, nirabhuga kweeki, muzomererwe!
\v 5 Obhunyoohu bhweenyu bhumenyekane kubhaatu bhoosi. Omukuru Yeesu ari haguhi kuuza.
\v 6 Mutige kwiitiimaata kwe ekigiro kyokyoosi, nawe kumangʼana goosi, kwo okusabha no okwiisasaama, hamwe no okubhuga, “Ozomirye,” obhweendi bhweetu bhumenyekane na Taatabhugya.
\v 7 Ambe, omureembe guno gukurwa ku Taatabhugya, guno gukuhita obhumenyi bhwoosi bhwa abhaatu, bhuriibhe eziikoro na amiiseego geenyu, kwo okugwaatana na Krisito Yeesu.
\p 
\v 8 Mubhuteero, abhahiiri bhaane, amangʼana go obhuheene, amangʼana gano gakweenderwa kusuukwa, amangʼana ge eheene, amangʼana gano gakyaari okwiisaanginia no obhubhi, amangʼana gano gakuzomera, amangʼana amazomu, amangʼana gano gakweenderwa okukumibhwa, mugiiseege amangʼana gayo.
\v 9 Mugeenderere kukora gano mweegiri no okusuungʼaana okurwa kweenye, gano mukiigwa nibhugiri, kweeki mukarora nigakoriri. Niho, Taatabhugya wuno akubhaha omureembe arageenderera kubha hamwe neemwe.
\s1 Pauro arabhabhuurira Abhafiripi “Ozomirye”
\p 
\v 10 Nizomereerwe bhukongʼu kwo okugwaatana no Omukuru Yeesu, kwo okubha mubhuteero, mutaangiri kweeki okuniiseegera enye. Nimenyiri kubha eziisiku zyoosi mwaari muraniseegera, nawe mutamirwe enzira yo okutumania obhusakirya bhweenyu kweenye.
\v 11 Nitakugaambeego kwe ekigirirye nino obhweendi, zeyi. Enye niegiri okwiiswa mwiibhaga ryoryoosi.
\v 12 Kweego nimenyiri okusuuhirwa ebhigiro, kweeki nimenyiri okubhona ebhigiro bhyaaru. Nimenyiri okwiiswa kwiibhaga ryo okubha ne ebhyaakurya bhyaaru kasi rye enzara, eraabhe eriibhaga ryo obhuniibhi kasi ryo okusuuhirwa.
\v 13 Niranagya kukora goosi gayo, kwo okubha Krisito niwe akuuniha amanaga.
\p 
\v 14 Naabhe ego, mukakora bhuzomu okugwaatana neenye munyaako yino niari nayo.
\v 15 Kyeego mumenyiri emwe Abhafiripi, hano nataangiri okubharwaazira Amangʼana Amazomu, na hano narwiiri mukyaaro kyeenyu kya Makedonia, emwe abheene niimwe mwaari muranisakirya. Ekanisa yeenyu eyeene niyo yaari no obhugwaatani neenye kwo okuruusya no okusuungʼaana ebhigiro.
\v 16 Naabhe hano niari mumugye gwa Tesaronike, muhaanitumira enye ebhigiro bhyo okunisakirya.
\v 17 Nitakugaambeego kwo okubha ndeenda okusuungʼaana ebhigiro okurwa kweemwe, zeyi. Nawe niseegiri nirore orubhaango runo Taatabhugya araabhahe kutuukana no obhusaambaaruku bhweenyu.
\p 
\v 18 Bhoono, ebhigiro bhirya bhyoosi bhino mukamuha Epafurodito okunireetera, nibhisuungʼaaniri. Bhiisiri mubhweendi bhwaane bhwoosi, kweeki ni kukiraho kyaabhurya niari kweenda. Obhusakirya bhuyo bhubheeri kyeego ekimweeso kino kikuraangasira bhuzomu, ekimweeso kino kiikiririibhwe no okumuzomera Taatabhugya.
\v 19 Ambe, Taatabhugya waane arabhaha obhweendi bhweenyu bhwoosi kuriingʼaana no obhuniibhi bhwaaye obhukuru. Arakora ego kwe enzira ya Krisito Yeesu.
\p 
\v 20 Taatabhugya Taata weetu, aguungibhwe kirakeego na kirakeego. Gabhe ego.
\s1 Amangʼana go obhuteero
\p 
\v 21 Mubhakeerye abhahoreeru bhoosi bha Firipi kwo okugwaatana na Krisito Yeesu. Abhiikirirya abharikyaane bhano bhari hamwe neenye bharabhakeerya emwe.
\v 22 Kweeki, abhahoreeru bhoosi bhano bhakwiikara mumugye guyo bharabhakeerya, kiindi bhano bhakukora emirimo munyuumba ya Kaisari.\f + \fr 4:22 \fk Kaisari \ft gwaari ni mweeya gwo omutemi omukuru gwa Abharooma. Yaari arakaangata ebhyaaro bhyaaru kwe enzira yo obhukorooni, naabhe ekyaaro kya Iziraeri. Rora engʼana yino mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f*
\p 
\v 23 Orubhaango rwo Omukuru weetu Yeesu Krisito, rubhe hamwe neemwe. Gabhe ego!
